EARNINGS AND PROVIDES OTHER DEREGULATORY BENEFITS FOR VERIZON NEW YORKS OPERATIONS IN CONNECTICUT. A PETITION TO EXTEND THE EFFECTIVE DATE OF THAT PLAN IS CURRENTLY PENDING.

