ASSUMED FUTURE RESULTS OF OPERATIONS. FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS ALSO INCLUDE THOSE PRECEDED OR FOLLOWED BY THE WORDS ANTICIPATES, BELIEVES, ESTIMATES, HOPES OR SIMILAR EXPRESSIONS. FOR THOSE

STATEMENTS, WE CLAIM THE PROTECTION OF THE SAFE HARBOR FOR FORWARD-LOOKING STATEMENTS CONTAINED IN THE PRIVATE SECURITIES LITIGATION REFORM ACT OF 1995.

